The wait is finally over we are back with a new Batch.

8 BASIC TO ADVANCE PROFESSIONAL MAKEUP COURSE 

Day 1 : PRODUCTS AND TOOLS KNOWLEDGE 
Theory & in-depth knowledge of Makeup products,  hairstyle products & other tools.

Day 2 : BUSINESS COUNSELLING 
Career & business counselling to help you make a triumphant professional.  Alongside, we shall enrich your photography techniques & clientele management.

Day 3 : HALDI LOOK 
Grab the attention with the Haldi look with the perfect assortment of floral touch to make the occasion glamorous.

Day 4 : MEHENDI LOOK 
Eye-catchy Mehendi/Sangeet look, Messy Braid, Fish Braid & suchlike skills will be part of the session.

Day 5 : Engagement look 
Learn to create Princess engagement look to mesmerise the crowd with your magic on the bride.

Day 6: NIKAH LOOK
Learn to bestow the flawless touch with your magic-brush fir the "Qabool hai" moment.

Day 7: RECEPTION LOOK 
Learn to create the perfect Wedding reception & bridal look as per the combination of reception outfit.

Day 8 : PAKISTANI BRIDAL LOOK 
Become proficient in the irresistible Pakistani bridal look.

Followed by Certification and Portfolio shoot.

Note : Products and Tools will be provided in class for practical purposes, one on one session will take place daily. 

ALL THE SKILLS, TECHNIQUES AND OTHER DETAILS WILL BE TAUGHT BY 
……………..AYESHA ABDULLA………………..
